OL,6,FThe research by the Policy Institute
OL,7,Fat King's College London also
OL,8,Fhighlights shifts in how much men
OL,9,Fcontribute to housework, the
OL,10,Fimportance of children doing homework,
OL,11,Fand the desire for higher wages over
OL,12,Fjob security.
OL,14,FProfessor Bobby Duffy, director of The
OL,15,FPolicy Institute, said: "These long-
OL,16,Fterm trends tell us so much about
OL,17,Felements of life we take for granted
OL,18,Ftoday but are actually pretty new in
OL,19,Four history."
